xyz.fsgik.common.bean.handlers

Class RecordBeanResolveHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.fsgik.common.bean.handlers.AbstractBeanResolveHandler
      • xyz.fsgik.common.bean.handlers.RecordBeanResolveHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FsBeanResolver.Handler

    public class RecordBeanResolveHandler
extends AbstractBeanResolveHandler
    Resolve handler for the record type object of which getters' name are equal to properties' name, and setters' name are start with "set" (same with JavaBeanResolveHandler).

    Note these methods will not be resolved to properties:

    • The methods which are declared by Object and not overridden;
    • toString() and hashCode();
